<p>investigation of enforced disappearances; to ensure that civil courts have jurisdiction over 
all matters relating to enforced disappearances; to establish a national search programme 
for missing persons with a protocol for immediate action; to guarantee the right to full 
reparation for the victims of enforced disappearance. 
</p>
